==============
INSTALLING FOAM
==============

1. Requirements
---------------

* One (or more) GNU/Linux Debian-like* system.

Note: for none Debian-like OSs you will have to manually install components since
OCF ofver-based [http://code.google.com/p/pypelib/] installation scripts only
support Debian-like OSs currently.

cd ./ofam --> check info-code inside


2. Installation of FOAM
---------------------------------------------------

https://github.com/fp7-ofelia/ocf/wiki/ofam-configuration (second part of webpage)


3. Upgrade instructions
-----------------------

https://github.com/fp7-ofelia/ocf/wiki/ofam-configuration (second part of webpage)


4. Additional notes
-------------------

Integration with ofelia.stable pending (almost ready), but OFAM fully functional and 
capable of interacting with legacy Expedient.


===============
FURTHER READING
===============

For more information about configuration, troubleshooting, contribution and
more please visit: https://github.com/fp7-ofelia/ocf/wiki/ofam-configuration

